Xegesis,is,a,sports,content,generation,system,built,to,allow,the,expansion,of,a,set,of,data,into,a,narrative,Xegesis,currently,focuses,on,soccer,but,intends,to,create,the,needed,text,analysis,to,support,multiple,sports,in,multiple,languages,The,Xegesis,API,provides,a,RESTful,interface,for,automating,access,and,publishing,of,Xegesis,generated,content,Responses,may,be,JSON,or,XML,formatted